<i>his motives for killing
teacher Amy Masterson</i>

15:03.486 --> 15:05.570
<i>and the kidnapping of Megan Rose.</i>

15:05.571 --> 15:08.490
<i>We go back live to join
reporter Alison Peretsky,</i>

15:08.491 --> 15:12.494
<i>who has been at the scene since law
enforcement officials arrived.</i>

15:12.495 --> 15:13.596
<i>Thank you, Jamie.</i>

15:13.621 --> 15:16.665
<i>It's now approximately four hours
