me in three blinks of an eye?</i>

16:46.589 --> 16:49.299
I'm not that easy.

16:49.300 --> 16:52.870
But with a little patience
and a little help,

16:52.887 --> 16:55.206
you just might profile me to a T.

16:56.599 --> 16:58.372
What makes you think
I'm interested?

17:00.603 --> 17:04.173
They say that when
I die, the case will die.

17:05.983 --> 17:08.551
They say it will be like
a book that I closed.

