<i>mailbox.</i>

17:31.801 --> 17:34.871
It's time to get back
to work, Dr Cross.

18:22.643 --> 18:25.061
<i>I have been planning
for a long, long time</i>

18:25.062 --> 18:28.132
<i>to involve you in the fate
