Secret Service detail at Cathedral.

19:58.656 --> 20:00.724
- Dr Cross.
- Agent Flannigan.

20:00.741 --> 20:03.094
I've read your books on profiling.

20:03.119 --> 20:06.063
Obviously not close enough, but...

20:07.456 --> 20:12.437
Kyle, this shoe was IDed by
the Roses. It's Megan's.

20:12.461 --> 20:15.235
Dr Alex Cross, Special
Agent in Charge...

20:15.256 --> 20:17.279
- Oliver McArthur.
- How do you do, sir?

20:17.299 --> 20:19.276
Alex, I'll catch you later.

20:19.301 --> 20:21.278
- Forensics.
- Yes, sir.

20:21.679 --> 20:24.282
The Senator and Mrs
Rose are through here.

20:25.141 --> 20:26.914
But before we talk to them,

20:26.934 --> 20:29.913
have you any idea why
Soneji is involving you?

20:29.937 --> 20:31.789
Not at all.

20:31.814 --> 20:33.587
This way.

20:33.607 --> 20:36.651
