our daughter didn't call you,

23:24.945 --> 23:28.323
so your agenda is what, to
insult the man he did call?

23:28.324 --> 23:32.270
- Mrs Rose, I never intended...
- No, you wait a second.

23:32.286 --> 23:34.037
A mad man has our daughter

23:34.038 --> 23:37.108
